=============================================================================================
VIEW TEST DOCUMENTATION HTML
=============================================================================================

You can start a local server to test the html file

METHOD 1:

* Navigate: cd voxility_pro/resources/documentation/
* Execute: python3 -m http.server
* Browser: https://http://localhost:8000

METHOD 2:

* Install Live Server extension on VSCode
* Open HTML file in VSCode
* Run Ctrl + Shift + P > "Live Server: Open with Live Server"
* http://127.0.0.1:5500/resources/documentation/voxility-documentation.html

=============================================================================================
MODIFY DOCUMENTATION
=============================================================================================

* Edit "voxility-content-test.html" which is included in "voxility-documentation.html"
* Test output via METHOD 2 with HTML document "voxility-documentation.html"
* run script "generate-documentation-content-html.sh" from project root
* copy contents from "voxility-content-final.html" to blendermarket.com documentation

